1
00:00:06,680 --> 00:00:07,800
The police have some questions to ask.

2
00:00:07,800 --> 00:00:09,280
Qiang, who is it?

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:11,280
Looks like the police.

4
00:00:11,400 --> 00:00:13,130
It's nothing. Go back to sleep.

5
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:14,200
So annoying.

6
00:00:14,920 --> 00:00:16,920
I told you it wasn't a good time.

7
00:00:16,920 --> 00:00:17,760
They're busy.

8
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:19,880
Sorry to bother you.

9
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:20,520
Just asking,

10
00:00:20,520 --> 00:00:21,200
from last night until now,

11
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:23,260
did you hear anything from next door?

12
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,400
No.

13
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:27,320
Did a man and a woman come next door recently?

14
00:00:27,320 --> 00:00:30,180
You mean those two who brought the restaurant over?

15
00:00:30,680 --> 00:00:32,200
They left last night.

16
00:00:32,400 --> 00:00:34,480
Did they leave together?

17
00:00:34,480 --> 00:00:36,600
Did anyone else come looking for them?

18
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:37,200
Officer,

19
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:39,040
are you the police or am I?

20
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:40,520
There were two of them when they came,

21
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:42,240
so there were two when they left.

22
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:44,320
How would I know if anyone came looking for them?

23
00:00:44,320 --> 00:00:45,000
Yes.

24
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:46,280
Anything else?

25
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:48,530
Nothing else. Sorry to bother you.

26
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:52,800
Good to know you're bothering us. So annoying.

27
00:00:57,680 --> 00:00:58,840
Let me ask you something.

28
00:00:58,840 --> 00:00:59,700
What time is it?

29
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:02,120
Don't you have a watch?

30
00:01:03,680 --> 00:01:06,480
If you don't answer, I'll have to ask someone else.

31
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:12,160
What's wrong now?

32
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,800
He just won't stop.

33
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:15,680
I have another question for you.

34
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:16,610
Hurry up and ask.

35
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:17,520
What time is it now?

36
00:01:17,520 --> 00:01:19,800
What time? You actually care about the time?

37
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:20,720
Nice watch.

38
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,840
Fake. It's a fake watch.

39
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:25,600
Qiangzai, who is it this time?

40
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,200
It's us again.

41
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,000
You guys again.

42
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:28,880
It's us.

43
00:01:29,080 --> 00:01:30,640
Look at your boyfriend. He is so handsome.

44
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:32,200
He looks good even with a fake watch.

45
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:34,400
We are going to have him take us to buy one.

46
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:36,520
Your boyfriend can't stay with you anymore.

47
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:36,880
Let's go.

48
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:39,680
Officer, wearing a fake watch isn't illegal, right?

49
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,039
Where are you taking him?

50
00:01:41,039 --> 00:01:42,000
Officer.

51
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,000
I had a bad attitude just now.

52
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:43,840
I just woke up.

53
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:44,920
I'm still not fully awake.

54
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,000
Not awake at all.

55
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:48,400
Don't worry, we'll wake you up soon enough.

56
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,479
This watch isn't mine.

57
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,970
Sister Qin gave it to me.

58
00:01:58,759 --> 00:02:00,200
You're suspected of running an illegal business.

59
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:02,880
and for organizing, participating in, and leading a triad-style organization,

60
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:04,080
we are arresting you in accordance with the law.

61
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:04,880
Take him away.

62
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:05,720
Officer,

63
00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:07,000
I have something to say.

64
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,080
If we make up for our crimes with good deeds,

65
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,280
can we get a lighter sentence?

66
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,560
Do you think you're in a costume drama?

67
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,160
A lighter sentence? Where to?

68
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,490
We caught two suspects.

69
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,400
Jun.

70
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,020
Wanted criminals.

71
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:22,440
Where did you leave them?

72
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,760
In the middle of nowhere.

73
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:26,240
Who would remember the way?

74
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,440
They are wanted criminals,

75
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:28,600
murderers.

76
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,410
I suggest you think carefully.

77
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:35,280
Take responsibility for yourself.

78
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,640
Hua.

79
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:36,920
Aiyuan.

80
00:03:41,440 --> 00:03:42,840
Aiyuan.

81
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:55,240
What did you do to me?

82
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,280
Tough guy.

83
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:59,500
But you might not be able to get hard anymore.

84
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:04,160
I took one of your kidneys.

85
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,560
But it's okay.

86
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,880
I left you one.

87
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:11,320
It won't affect your normal life.

88
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:18,399
But as for your lives,

89
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:21,040
I'm not so sure.

90
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:28,360
But I can take you out to sell yourself.

91
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:32,159
There are lots of men there who can satisfy you.

92
00:04:32,159 --> 00:04:33,480
Aiyuan.

93
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:38,360
You really look like a hooker.

94
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:42,760
You don't even have the assets to sell.

95
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:44,620
Kill me today if you have the guts!

96
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:47,159
Are you okay?

97
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:50,159
Qin.

98
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:53,640
Should we just off them both?

99
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:57,040
Jun and I are businesspeople.

100
00:04:57,280 --> 00:04:58,280
We can have blood on our hands,

101
00:04:58,280 --> 00:04:59,610
but we don't take lives.

102
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:01,280
They are both wanted criminals.

103
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:02,520
Kill them?

104
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:03,960
Don't bring trouble upon ourselves.

105
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:05,480
Use your brain more.

106
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:06,560
Right.

107
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,560
Qin is right.

108
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:10,040
I know you're not afraid of them.

109
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:12,140
But I'm really afraid of his revenge.

110
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:14,000
In the middle of nowhere,

111
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,000
leaving them here

112
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,970
is no different from killing them.

113
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:22,760
Right in that

114
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:26,960
abandoned warehouse at Yehu Ridge.

115
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,159
I found it out.

116
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:37,080
They dumped them in an abandoned warehouse near Yehu Ridge.

117
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:38,960
But that place is too far from us.

118
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:43,159
I'll immediately notify the comrades near Yehu Ridge to investigate.

119
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:44,400
Okay. Thanks.

120
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:01,960
Right here.

121
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:18,570
They got away again.

122
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:20,940
Hurry up and secure the scene.

123
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:04,160
Aiyuan, go.

124
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,560
Run as far as you can.

125
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:10,800
Otherwise, neither of us can leave when the police come.

126
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:15,480
I can't make it out with this wound.

127
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:17,880
Go!

128
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:26,000
Go!

129
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,610
Don't make yourself regret it.

130
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:37,800
I'll go,

131
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:42,000
but I have a question for you.

132
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,320
Ask.

133
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:46,600
After I answer, you leave.

134
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:50,680
The day I asked Hong Jinyi to the rental house,

135
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:58,480
were you late on purpose?

136
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:05,600
Brother, I think it's about time.

137
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,720
Let's go up.

138
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,680
Wait a bit.

139
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:15,880
Yes.

140
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:19,160
Why?

141
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,320
I'm sorry.

142
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,360
I know someone like me

143
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:31,220
isn't good enough for you.

144
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:35,240
So I thought,

145
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:38,360
if I didn't drag you down,

146
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:42,240
you wouldn't be willing to stay with me.

147
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:47,280
But I just love you too much.

148
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,760
I was afraid I couldn't keep you.

149
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:56,080
That's it.

150
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:57,560
You can go now.

151
00:08:57,560 --> 00:09:00,080
Go!

152
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:05,360
Go!
